version_description:
NEW STUFF!

- Enhanced Respawn Screen - New details about who defeated you, so you can plan your revenge
- Boss Room progress bars - It’s now easier to tell how close you or the other team are to winning!
- Small UI updates to end-of-match screen
- Fixed issue affecting some players' ability to connect to game in certain network conditions
- Some UI issues fixed - not every freshly unlocked weapon is named Royal Sword, we promise
- Lots of other bugs squashed, we smashed them with our feet AND our hands
